datasets.name: 3696faf2
queryLines:
select
  name,
  date(`timestamp`) as date,
  max(`average`) as avg,
  avg(`maximum`) as avg_max,
  max(`maximum`) as max_max
from
  IDENTIFIER(:target_catalog || '.' || :target_schema || '.metrics_dedicated_pool_metrics')
where
  name in ('DWUUsedPercent', 'DWU used percentage', 'DWU percentage')
group by
  name,
  date(`timestamp`)
order by
  name
